<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA526_06_IH_0002_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema526_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema526_06_ih_0002">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">회전판을 돌릴 때 화살이 보라색에 멈출 가능성이 높은 순서대로 <span class="empty_box nemo"></span>안에 1, 2, 3, 4를 써넣으세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_60">
          <div class="flex dir_col align_center gap_60">
            <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA526_06_IH/0002_img1.svg" alt="" /></div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex dir_col align_center gap_60">
            <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA526_06_IH/0002_img2.svg" alt="" /></div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="1"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex dir_col align_center gap_60">
            <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA526_06_IH/0002_img3.svg" alt="" /></div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="2"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex dir_col align_center gap_60">
            <div class="img"><img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA526_06_IH/0002_img4.svg" alt="" /></div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="3"></math-field>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">회전판에서 보라색 부분이 넓을수록 화살이 보라색에 멈출 가능성이 높습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
